messages.content: 9-1-1, what's your emergency?
Yes, ma'am. I think my son's been killed.
Where at?
We're in the Evergreen Trailer Park on Bolson Street, Trailer 81.
Okay, what's the exact address?
Walton Street, Trailer 81, Evergreen Trailer Park in North Canton.
Is it in North Canton City?
Yes, it is in North Canton City.
Alright, stay on the line, okay? It's not coming up on my map, so I want to make sure we get the right place.
Stay on the line.
Okay.
North Canton emergency.
Yes, this is Judy Smith. I'm at my son's trailer park.
Uh-huh.
We just broke in and it looks like he's in the bathroom, but his head's missing.
Wait, what? His head isn’t there?
I know it sounds really weird, but...
Wait a minute. You’re in his trailer, and you see him in the bathroom?
It looks like him. I don't know.
Could you just dispatch an officer?
Yeah, we'll send an officer.
There's a body or something there. It looks like his legs.
Okay. Alright. We'll have an officer up there, all right?
Okay. Thank you.
